{"tid":2331650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聲援黎智英｜柯文哲：臨危不逃有氣魄 拘捕照激發台灣更強反中情緒","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T04:01:31.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0921cd90da9c482cd511a99d600fe7e79b851f","tid":2331650,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XR9WUVy9W8grtJJ1Z0eRO0xzU0w=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6M3UC4QF45DT5FH6JIEQXV5PAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXR9WUVy9W8grtJJ1Z0eRO0xzU0w%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6M3UC4QF45DT5FH6JIEQXV5PAE.jpg&h=2d248364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被拘柙已17日，且在昨晨（18日）被轉送到高設防的赤柱監獄。各界繼續聲援黎智英，台灣台北市長柯文哲形容，黎智英身為大商家，寧可放棄攜錢出走，也要堅持理念留港，是很有氣魄。他又指看到黎的被捕、被警方鎖上鐵鏈手銬的照片，只會激起台灣更大的反中情緒。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲表示在看到黎智英被警方鎖上鐵鏈、手扣的畫面，覺得是北京當局進行的一種恐嚇，不過從「北風跟太陽」的童話故事可以知道，強硬的手段不會使人民屈服，相信這種動作不會對壓止香港人民反抗有實質效果，只會令香港的問題更嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n他指，黎智英身為大老闆，「本可帶着錢遠走海外，舒服過日子」，但他選擇留在香港繼續堅持他的理念、表達自己的想法，所以覺得他很有氣魄，代表他是一個很有個性、很有想法的人。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲表示，現在的世界是個地球村，黎智英遭逮捕這張照片傳出去，只會增加全世界反中的情緒。<br />\n<br />\n台灣方面，他指因距港更近，反應自然會更大，且台灣的反中情緒自去年香港反送中運動以後，只有增加沒有減少，黎智英被捕的照片傳出後，台灣反中情緒也會更加激烈。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲強調，從整個人類歷史的經驗看，打壓不會解決問題，就像大禹治水，幾千年前的智慧可見，「圍堵不會解決氾濫，只有疏導才會」，一昧打壓只是讓人民反彈更嚴重而已。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》"},{"pid":"2d79023d576c1108f23d62257b14f8590ce9ec86","tid":2331650,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/LIZALW6TGBHPZHKPT54HT7MBGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FLIZALW6TGBHPZHKPT54HT7MBGU%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7e3390c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FLIZALW6TGBHPZHKPT54HT7MBGU%2F&h=4a3d7dd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/LIZALW6TGBHPZHKPT54HT7MBGU/</a>"},{"pid":"9374ff22706f6ec269ce2e682d98bcc8222be184","tid":2331650,"uid":250979,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"究極共謀真係識講野"},{"pid":"71cc1eb7133bbd273ff0a1eec656060c838594ed","tid":2331650,"uid":83713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3nZsrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3nZsrz.jpg&h=5b163940&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e0f631f27030cd584d97e7722af1513247f3847","tid":2331650,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎，多謝你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e45f0aa267104bd02519d648c8714fbaf02718","tid":2331650,"uid":342855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"呢隻檳榔收皮啦"},{"pid":"d847132637520db8419f7b26a9911e9c0850602d","tid":2331650,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71cc1eb7133bbd273ff0a1eec656060c838594ed","tid":2331650,"uid":83713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3nZsrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3nZsrz.j